description: Just one day before Christmas I again decided to check my favourite shopping centre for some cute boys. After I waited for about 15 minutes I finally found the typ of guy I am usually looking for. He was actually kinda overcautious. He didn´t even want to tell me his name nor where he works. Anyway, he started to listen a bit more careful when I told him that I have a model agency and there was some money to be made. I somehow convinced him that I need to make a short casting with him. Of course I had to promising money for it. But when we arrived at the hotel he didn´t even want to show me his dick.
title: Czech Hunter 122
